# Logic in Robot Car

![../60-Meta-Attachments/50526155c21e9d5827e02362daabc134.png](data:image/png;base64,)

> [!note]
> Title: L_Sensor & R_sensor
> 0: Sensor on **White**
> 1: Sensor on **Black**

> [!note]
> Title: L_DIR & R_DIR
> 0: DIR backward
> 1: DIR forward

| Sensor   |          | Expected Car motor actions |             | Left motor control | Right motor control |
| -------- | -------- | -------------------------- | ----------- | ------------------ | ------------------- |
| L_Sensor | R_Sensor | Left motor                 | Right motor | L_DIR              | R_DIR               |
| 0        | 0        | Forward                    | backward    | 1                  | 1                   |
| 0        | 1        | forward                    | backward    | 1                  | 0                   |
| 1        | 0        | backward                   | forward     | 0                  | 1                   |
| 1        | 1        | backward                   | forward     | 0                  | 0                   |
